groups:
  group avatars
  group renderers

game management:
  add/remove user to game by admin
  add/remove fake player to game by admin
  close game providing results
  restrict game date created by regular group member

post authoring:
  restrict post editing
  post privacy should be independent of group privacy

forms:
  hints in forms
  required fields
  input time in a textfield with chronic gem (railscast 32)

other:
  pagination
  use paranoid mass assignment protection
  dependent => :destroy on joining models (railscast 167)


VULNERABILITIES:
  any user can be added to a game through nested attributes


